  <title><literal>GetGroupCount()</literal></title>

  <indexterm significance="preferred">
    <primary>Dialplan-Applikationen</primary>

    <secondary><code>GetGroupCount()</code></secondary>
  </indexterm>

  <simpara>Returns the number of channels in a channel group.</simpara>

  <synopsis>GetGroupCount(<replaceable>group</replaceable>[@<replaceable>category</replaceable>])</synopsis>

  <important>
    <para><literal>GetGroupCount()</literal> is removed as of Asterisk 1.4 and
    has been replaced by the <literal>GROUP_COUNT()</literal> (<xref
    linkend="functions-group_count" />) function.</para>
  </important>

